%p Hello #{@resource.email}!
%p Someone has requested a link to change your password. You can do this through the link below.
%p
  - return_option = (@resource.reset_password_return_url.present? ? "?return_url=#{@resource.reset_password_return_url}" : "" )
  - if ConsumerApp.current.present?
    - url = Thread.current[:consumer_app].uri + '/forgot-password/' + @token + return_option
  - else
    - url = edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) + return_option
  = link_to 'Change my password', url

%p If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.
%p Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.
